@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber

actor "Unregistered User" as User
participant ":System" as System

activate User

    User -> System : requests to list properties
    activate System
    deactivate System


    alt Filter and Sort

        System --> User : shows type of property options (House, Apartement or Land) and requests user to choose
        activate System
        deactivate System

        User -> System : selects type of property
        activate System

        System --> User : shows type of business options (Sale or Rent) and requests user to choose
        deactivate System

        User -> System : selects type of business
        activate System

        System --> User : shows number of rooms options (1, 2, 3, 4 or 5) filter and requests user to choose
        deactivate System

        User -> System : selects number of rooms
        activate System

        System -> User : shows sort criterias (Price, City or State) and requests user to choose
        deactivate System

        User -> System : selects sort criteria
        activate System

        System --> User : shows order options (Ascending or Descending) and requests user to choose
        deactivate System

        User -> System : selects order
        activate System

        System --> User : shows filter and sort options selected by user and requests confirmation
        deactivate System

    else Filter or Sort

        alt Filter

            System --> User : shows filter and sort options
            activate System
            deactivate System

            User -> System : selects filter options but doesn't select sort options
            activate System

            System --> User : shows that properties will be filtered using filter options selected by user, \n sorted by default sort criteria (most recently added) and requests confirmation
            deactivate System
        else Sort
            System --> User : shows filter and sort options
            activate System
            deactivate System

            User -> System : selects sort options but doesn't select filter options
            activate System

            System --> User : shows that all properties will be listed with sort criteria selected by user
            deactivate System
        end


    else Neither Filter nor Sort
        System --> User : shows filter and sort options
        activate System
        deactivate System

        User -> System : neither selects filter options nor sort options
        activate System

        System --> User : shows that all properties will be listed with default sort criteria (most recently added) and requests confirmation
        deactivate System


    end

    User -> System : confirms selection
    activate System

    System --> User : displays the respective list of properties
    deactivate System




@enduml